title: Hour 3 - Charles Barkley Playing LIV Pro/Am, Doubts About Kyler Murray
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Charles Barkley Playing LIV Pro/Am, Doubts About Kyler Murray
description:
Dan discusses the inevitability that Charles Barkley ends up working for the LIV Golf Tour after playing in their upcoming Pro/Am. And he worries that the Cardinals overpaid for Kyler Murray.
